custom_fields.label: PreCheck Comments
custom_fields.mandatory_depends_on:
eval:doc.custom_vehicle_interior == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_ac_operations == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_lights == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_battery_condition == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_wire_condition == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_whipers == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_indicators == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_warning_lights == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_power_windows == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_dashboard_condition == 'Faulty' || 
			doc.custom_speedometer == 'Faulty';
custom_fields.name: Installation Note-custom_installation_comments

custom_fields.label: Post Installation Comments
custom_fields.mandatory_depends_on:
eval:doc.custom_tracker_grounded == 0 || 
			doc.custom_url_configured == 0 || 
			doc.custom_assigned_to_customer_tenant == 0 ||
			doc.custom_vehicle_assigned_to_user == 0 || 
			doc.custom_closed_vehicle == 0 || 
			doc.custom_informed_driver_to_move_vehicle == 0  ||	
			doc.custom_used_cable_ties_ == 0;
custom_fields.name: Installation Note-custom_post_installation_comments
